title: The.Great.British.Children.in.Need.Sewing.Bee.S01E03.PDTV.x264-J
description:
The Great British Children in Need Sewing Bee - Series 1, Episode 3




Anita Rani completes the hosting line-up for episode 3 and is joined by BBC Radio 1 DJ Gemma Cairney, comedian Helen Lederer, TV critic and author Kathryn Flett, and Overtones singer Timmy Matley. The challenges certainly get the celebrities thinking creatively, as they're tasked with creating a junior garment inspired by their own favourite childhood memory.




Original Air Date: 24-Oct-2014
